<template><div><h2 id="概述" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#概述"><span>概述</span></a></h2>
<p>主题内置的代码高亮插件， 对代码块进行代码高亮。</p>
<p>关联插件：<a href="https://ecosystem.vuejs.press/zh/plugins/markdown/shiki.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@vuepress/plugin-shiki</a></p>
<p>主题 使用 <a href="https://github.com/shikijs/shiki" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Shiki</a> 在 Markdown 代码块中使用彩色文本实现语法高亮。
Shiki 支持多种编程语言。</p>
<p>在 Shiki 的代码仓库中，可以找到 <a href="https://shiki.style/languages" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">合法的编程语言列表</a> 。</p>
<h2 id="特性" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#特性"><span>特性</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li><RouteLink to="/notes/theme/guide/code/features.html#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%9D%97%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98">代码块标题</RouteLink></li>
<li><RouteLink to="/notes/theme/guide/code/features.html#%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%9D%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E8%A1%8C%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%AE">代码行高亮</RouteLink></li>
<li><RouteLink to="/notes/theme/guide/code/features.html#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%9D%97%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%9A%E7%84%A6">代码聚焦</RouteLink></li>
<li><RouteLink to="/notes/theme/guide/code/features.html#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%9D%97%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E5%B7%AE%E5%BC%82">代码对比差异</RouteLink></li>
<li><RouteLink to="/notes/theme/guide/code/features.html#%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%AE-%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF-%E5%92%8C-%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A">代码高亮“错误”和“警告”</RouteLink></li>
<li><RouteLink to="/notes/theme/guide/code/features.html#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%9D%97%E4%B8%AD-%E8%AF%8D%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%AE">代码词高亮</RouteLink></li>
<li><RouteLink to="/notes/theme/guide/code/features.html#%E6%8A%98%E5%8F%A0%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%9D%97">代码块折叠</RouteLink></li>
<li><RouteLink to="/notes/theme/guide/code/twoslash.html#twoslash">twoslash</RouteLink> ：在代码块内提供内联类型提示。</li>
</ul>
